Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,（98堂Artist）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你要睡到什么時候，快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.06,0:00:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再睡5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,又撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.33,0:00:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,5分钟而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.27,0:00:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 要迟到了 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.47,0:00:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,5分钟我就起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 决定不行，快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行，快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.75,0:00:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,5分钟就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.08,0:00:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你老是这样，快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的，能赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,赶不上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,饭我都准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.96,0:00:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,话说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要晚归吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有个店我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,今于要和上司去喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.00,0:01:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,那就周末
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.87,0:01:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,说好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,等我回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃，要冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.69,0:01:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要\N就现在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.03,0:02:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,快吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.96,0:02:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,下次出去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.17,0:02:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呢\N和食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,和食吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.98,0:02:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那家正宗的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我会加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.18,0:02:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,给\N谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,好走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不要喝太多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.61,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,在老公之外的肉棒下\N丧失自我的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,进来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,太太，不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.97,0:03:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他有点喝多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思，要你送回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.91,0:03:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,老公没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.51,0:03:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我也让他多喝了，对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.92,0:03:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吗，能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.59,0:03:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,能站起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.12,0:03:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.19,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种地方不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,帮我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.06,0:03:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,给我爬到床上去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.40,0:03:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.74,0:03:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.81,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,数日后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.41,0:04:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,古城先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.76,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,说一下你老公的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.11,0:04:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,老公还没回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.05,0:04:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你的老公是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.99,0:04:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,他不会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,说这种话，我很为难的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.46,0:04:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不要为难
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我才为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.33,0:04:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我会负责的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,给我住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.61,0:05:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你懂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.35,0:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,都是你老公不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不要跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,给我老实一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.10,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不过很大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.17,0:05:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,住手啊，这样很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.70,0:05:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我才为难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，老实一些就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.13,0:05:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,给我老实点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,给 帮我摸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,太太怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在和你老公的比吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.23,0:06:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,靠近一些看 也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,和你老公的比
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.31,0:06:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的更大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事 我说不出
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.39,0:06:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,那就看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,果然很想看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.80,0:07:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒和老公的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的更大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,让我告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.76,0:07:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,上次喝酒他醉了后脱掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙的肉棒很小的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.65,0:08:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,很想摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不讨厌的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,讨厌的话可以说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.48,0:08:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,要告诉你老公吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.42,0:08:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.43,0:08:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,来玩弄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.17,0:08:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.71,0:08:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公大的肉棒不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.06,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个更大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.59,0:09:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,太太来回答吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这个更大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个比老公的...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,更大...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.42,0:09:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,说出来了呢，太太
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.77,0:10:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很想舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公的更大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,更肥...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,更硬...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.40,0:10:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,很想尝尝这个肉棒的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的哦，太太
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴张开了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,现在想舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.24,0:11:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.51,0:11:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,想舔我的肉棒的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.40,0:11:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,舔起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.55,0:11:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,超级大的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不能完全放进嘴里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,想要更多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.10,0:12:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想尝尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.10,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.77,0:12:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,想继续舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,很想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真的想舔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.34,0:12:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我的大肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.17,0:13:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.90,0:13:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,想要我的舌头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.79,0:13:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,快想象我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,插入小穴会有多爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.34,0:13:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.68,0:14:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,可是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.36,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我有老公啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.64,0:14:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这种牙签一样的肉棒可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.44,0:14:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能让你满足吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想要最爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,做爱体验吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.13,0:14:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 奶头都挺起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,奸漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这么挺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.84,0:15:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.85,0:15:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,快点摸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.53,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,太太很想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要玩弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.21,0:16:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 让我来玩弄你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,来我前面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,用屁股
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,尝尝肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,快点摩擦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股那里什么挺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的屁股碰到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,又肥又硬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.93,0:17:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到了超级硬的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.20,0:17:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,只是硬说不清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.47,0:17:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,硬的什么，告诉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.07,0:17:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.14,0:17:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.48,0:17:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,不是小孩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.95,0:17:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不是小鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.22,0:17:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,是肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.09,0:17:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,又肥又硬的...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.16,0:17:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒被我碰到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.97,0:17:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.12,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,身体很老实嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.53,0:18:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,这里也要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,知道自己的身体现在怎么样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊 这么湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.82,0:18:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,超级湿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,只是这样还不知道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,慢慢的汁液好湿才对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:18:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.91,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,说了就让你更爽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,被丈夫以外的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,男人摸了之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴变得好湿好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,很懂嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.34,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.81,0:19:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.95,0:19:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.48,0:19:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很寂寞的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.75,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,还不能去哦，太太
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,脱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,脱掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不脱掉，肉棒进不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,超级害羞的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的小穴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,被摸的很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,摸我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.63,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超级大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.64,0:21:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好想舔太太的小穴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很想舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,很想被舔的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那就舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,好好看着哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.82,0:21:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想舔更多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.36,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.16,0:22:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股也看的很清楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.77,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,老公都没有做过这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.77,0:22:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那以后我每天都让你\N保持这么淫荡的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,想高潮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.68,0:22:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.02,0:23:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好爽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.56,0:23:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.83,0:23:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.90,0:23:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,去了，要去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.41,0:23:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越习惯了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.36,0:24:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.30,0:24:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.44,0:24:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公就是这么小的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.71,0:24:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒插进去就是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.26,0:24:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不能满足的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.74,0:24:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,不多弄一些
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.67,0:25:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肥肉棒进不去的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.95,0:25:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.76,0:25:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行\N好紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.57,0:25:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.98,0:25:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那用力了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.45,0:25:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很淫荡的声音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.45,0:25:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,吧唧吧唧的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.59,0:25:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.86,0:26:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不行，不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.01,0:26:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.82,0:26:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.76,0:26:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.76,0:26:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.96,0:26:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,就是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.30,0:26:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.98,0:26:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴想要了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.80,0:27:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.88,0:27:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,再让你看一次哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.20,0:28:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，多加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.63,0:28:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好大，好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.11,0:28:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都要舔哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.38,0:29:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,才舔了一半呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.91,0:29:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的一半不吞进去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.79,0:29:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,老公都不用这么深
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.86,0:29:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我的要更深一些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.68,0:29:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,更多的...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.69,0:29:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不能全部插进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.97,0:30:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.30,0:30:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能全部插进去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.18,0:30:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.98,0:30:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴太小了，插不完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.39,0:30:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.33,0:30:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴不行的话
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.93,0:30:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,就这边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.40,0:30:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,插入小穴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.27,0:30:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都插进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.68,0:30:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公大太多了，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:45.75,0:30:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好了，尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.08,0:30:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,尝尝看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.89,0:30:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.82,0:30:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.15,0:30:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这么大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.89,0:30:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.56,0:31:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.03,0:31:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,进不去的，不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.71,0:31:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,插进深处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.92,0:31:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.66,0:31:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.93,0:31:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.14,0:31:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.21,0:31:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,插得好深啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.88,0:31:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.75,0:31:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.63,0:32:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.57,0:32:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,很奕的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.39,0:32:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,要更多哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.40,0:32:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.27,0:32:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.61,0:32:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还不够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.35,0:33:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.35,0:33:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.22,0:33:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,插进哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.69,0:33:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,插进小穴了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.89,0:33:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,要拔出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.56,0:33:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.78,0:33:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好大好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.65,0:33:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续插
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.45,0:33:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我就要坏掉了
