Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.20,0:41:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这样好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.67,0:41:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,完全看见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.87,0:41:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,插着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.67,0:41:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,看得好清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.43,0:42:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.31,0:42:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,老公没有这么猛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.31,0:42:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.58,0:42:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,插的好深哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.45,0:42:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.72,0:42:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.67,0:42:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.47,0:42:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,近一些...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.35,0:42:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的脸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.43,0:43:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.63,0:43:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.44,0:43:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,正面来插哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.72,0:43:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽的...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.47,0:43:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,多插一些哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.28,0:44:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的小穴张的好开哦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.88,0:44:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.55,0:44:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,会被老公发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.49,0:44:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么会被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.03,0:44:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.16,0:44:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴变宽了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.97,0:44:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.84,0:44:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,可是很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.85,0:44:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.31,0:44:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒很爽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这点没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.13,0:44:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,让我拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.20,0:44:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.14,0:45:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.14,0:45:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的肉棒和我的比 谁的大
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.35,0:45:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.55,0:45:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.82,0:45:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谁的更爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.36,0:45:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快点回答
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.09,0:45:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.83,0:45:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.43,0:45:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样老公很可怜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.70,0:45:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,跟老公道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.51,0:45:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,做了这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.71,0:45:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.78,0:45:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,老公对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.78,0:45:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,继续啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.18,0:45:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.92,0:45:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你之外的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.32,0:45:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,太有感觉了...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.67,0:46:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吗，没有要说的了？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.67,0:46:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,道歉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.41,0:46:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.81,0:46:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.81,0:46:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.01,0:46:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,又要去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.15,0:46:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你之外的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.95,0:46:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,比你的 更大的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.22,0:46:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,让我高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.22,0:46:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.83,0:46:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.23,0:46:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.24,0:46:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.84,0:46:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.97,0:46:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太爽了 受不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.38,0:46:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.59,0:46:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.87,0:47:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.13,0:47:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我也要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.47,0:47:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,要射好多出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.74,0:47:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.10,0:47:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,给我舔干净
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.81,0:48:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.28,0:48:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,之后也...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.61,0:48:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的玩耍哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.36,0:49:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.44,0:50:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,真的这样想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.44,0:50:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.98,0:50:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.45,0:50:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.59,0:50:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.12,0:50:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.06,0:50:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是这么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.80,0:50:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:39.07,0:50:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,给我删除掉
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.54,0:50:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.88,0:50:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.62,0:50:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就给你老公看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.62,0:50:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.76,0:50:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.90,0:51:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就听我的话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.84,0:51:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.57,0:51:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,老公不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.86,0:52:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.93,0:52:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不愿意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.14,0:52:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你会删除掉的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.74,0:52:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.34,0:52:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我会考虑的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.97,0:53:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:36.05,0:53:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.92,0:53:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看更大
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.17,0:54:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很棒的奶子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.18,0:54:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.88,0:55:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真是很棒的身体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.82,0:55:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,太太
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.36,0:55:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,果然还是很害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.36,0:55:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.77,0:55:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.51,0:55:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.59,0:55:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.19,0:55:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,不能随便吞了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.87,0:56:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在眼前的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.60,0:56:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.87,0:56:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事说不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.14,0:56:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.68,0:56:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.81,0:56:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,关上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.16,0:56:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.37,0:56:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,小鸡鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.50,0:56:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.17,0:56:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,说法不对
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.11,0:56:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒才对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.58,0:56:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好大...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.38,0:56:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好肥...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.99,0:57:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.99,0:57:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好长...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.39,0:57:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.86,0:57:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个和你老公的比怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.27,0:57:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的又小...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.34,0:57:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,又软...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.15,0:57:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,完全插不到深处...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:29.48,0:57:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,和你的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.16,0:57:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,想要这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.03,0:57:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,很喜欢我的肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.43,0:57:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,又肥又大的肉棒 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.51,0:57:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,关上好了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.78,0:57:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,想要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.98,0:58:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这个肉棒怎么才好，说说看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.73,0:58:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想要
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.46,0:58:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,想要舔个爽
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.41,0:58:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.88,0:58:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,和老公的完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.88,0:58:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,又大又硬的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.35,0:58:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,插进我的嘴里
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.10,0:58:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.90,0:58:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,不让我爽不可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.04,0:59:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,不好好的弄
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.71,0:59:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,关上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.72,0:59:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老公的...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.72,0:59:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,他人的 又肥又大的肉棒\N请让我来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.20,0:59:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.46,0:59:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.67,0:59:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那就来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.67,0:59:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,来舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.24,1:00:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.59,1:00:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,对 超级爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.94,1:00:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,开心吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.55,1:00:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在在舔的是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.09,1:00:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,又大...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.23,1:01:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,又硬...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.90,1:01:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又肥...又热....
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.10,1:01:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老公的，是别人的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.78,1:01:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,大肉棒很开心吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.92,1:01:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.79,1:01:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,要吞进喉咙深处哦
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.99,1:01:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,懂吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:52.28,1:01:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,超级棒的
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.83,1:02:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.58,1:02:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,真棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.18,1:02:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的好小...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.39,1:02:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,插不到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.19,1:02:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我的很容易插到吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.86,1:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,深处很有感觉吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.02,1:03:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.58,1:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒变硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.78,1:03:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,超级硬的
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.05,1:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好翘
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.25,1:03:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.82,1:04:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,舔了很多呢，满足了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.02,1:04:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.16,1:04:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可以了吧？舔了这么多
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.30,1:04:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.11,1:04:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,又热又硬...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.31,1:04:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,又长的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.25,1:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,想要肉棒插入我的小穴
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.92,1:04:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,想要插入吗？怎么样才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.32,1:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.73,1:04:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴想要吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.67,1:05:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,想要就说啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.54,1:05:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.67,1:05:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.67,1:05:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.61,1:05:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那就插入吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.88,1:05:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股朝向这边
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.70,1:05:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很想要吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.98,1:05:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,完全看见了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.19,1:05:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.99,1:05:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,又大又硬的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.06,1:05:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.86,1:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那就开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.93,1:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.80,1:06:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,碰到阴核了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.94,1:06:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插得好深，好爽
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.69,1:06:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这样不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.56,1:06:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.76,1:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,都已经在摩擦了，可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.56,1:06:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就满足了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.10,1:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就很爽了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.84,1:06:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.91,1:06:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,又大，又硬的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.31,1:06:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,插进深处吧
Dialogue: 0,1:06:56.05,1:06:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在摩擦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.65,1:06:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.59,1:07:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是还不够
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.72,1:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,插进来吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.40,1:07:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.53,1:07:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老公的...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.60,1:07:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,别人又大...又硬的...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.07,1:07:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.14,1:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,请插进...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.68,1:07:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小穴吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.35,1:07:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.82,1:07:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样已经很有感觉了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:07:35.96,1:07:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,还要更多...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.90,1:07:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,插着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.36,1:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这样可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.03,1:07:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.58,1:08:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴的深处
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.52,1:08:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.92,1:08:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.72,1:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,太小了...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.92,1:08:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.53,1:08:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢大的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.34,1:08:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,变软了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.23,1:08:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这样很爽，马上又硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:03.11,1:09:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样舔
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.66,1:09:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,超级爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.34,1:09:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这样超级爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.02,1:09:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,又硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.05,1:10:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,塞满了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.40,1:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,再激烈一些会更爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.90,1:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,对 就这样
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.41,1:11:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,对，多用力一些
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.07,1:12:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:46.80,1:12:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哦
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.94,1:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能射
Dialogue: 0,1:12:50.94,1:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为太爽了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.94,1:12:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不能射
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.01,1:12:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,请把又肥又大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.68,1:13:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,插入我的小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.95,1:13:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.49,1:13:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为老公的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.75,1:13:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的比老公的更大...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.89,1:13:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,更热...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.43,1:13:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,更硬的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.10,1:13:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,请插入我的小穴...\N插入深处
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.83,1:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.44,1:13:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.64,1:13:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,出来了
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.70,1:13:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不要射 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.79,1:14:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,请进
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.66,1:14:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.67,1:15:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,土屋先生的房子吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.20,1:15:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.94,1:15:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里签名可以吗\N好的
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.28,1:15:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.62,1:15:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才从你的熟人那里
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.23,1:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,得到了这个东西
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.68,1:16:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,太太真的很喜欢肉棒呢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.15,1:16:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，好大
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.22,1:16:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,大吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:28.49,1:16:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢大的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.03,1:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我好喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.16,1:16:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,又大又肥又硬的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:16:42.24,1:16:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,这个第一次见的肉棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:16:45.17,1:16:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.51,1:16:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,别人的肉棒可以
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.18,1:16:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的 满足不了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:05.19,1:17:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,这么喜欢的话
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.86,1:17:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那随便舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.89,1:17:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次见的人的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.49,1:17:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,可以这样子吸啊
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.97,1:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.38,1:17:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公在吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.92,1:18:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.92,1:18:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的太小了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.92,1:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你老公真可怜呢
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.87,1:18:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的太小
Dialogue: 0,1:18:24.07,1:18:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不能满足
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.01,1:18:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,又大...
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.74,1:18:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,又硬的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.41,1:18:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,才能插入深处
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.17,1:19:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,让我看看太太的脸
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.99,1:19:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,还要更兴奋哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.21,1:19:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒的奶子
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.09,1:19:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好好的吞肉棒吧
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.96,1:19:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.44,1:20:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,做更淫荡的事的话
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.70,1:20:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,会变得更大的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:18.05,1:20:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地舔吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.75,1:20:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,吞得好深 好爽哦
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.72,1:21:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,有这么喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.92,1:21:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,超级喜欢大大的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.66,1:21:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,又肥又硬的...
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.33,1:21:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,再吞深一些吧
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.33,1:21:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好的 摸太太的身体的
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.32,1:22:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,奶子好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.29,1:23:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,奶子爽吗
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.63,1:23:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.23,1:23:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这样子舔 很有感觉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.91,1:23:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,被别人...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.58,1:23:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,吸奶子...
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.84,1:23:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,超级有感觉的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.65,1:23:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.49,1:24:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,太太的身体真的好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.30,1:24:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真的好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.17,1:24:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,被别人摸 超级有感觉的
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.24,1:24:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴变得好湿好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.18,1:24:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,请多摸一些吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.43,1:25:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,摸这里可以吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.90,1:25:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,摸吧
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.10,1:25:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,只是摸就够了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.64,1:25:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,阴核很硬了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.18,1:25:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.65,1:25:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,让我的小穴更湿吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.26,1:26:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就这么湿了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.40,1:26:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次的也很好
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.80,1:26:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次见面
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.67,1:26:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,就被这样摸
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.08,1:26:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,超级有感觉的
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.22,1:26:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,老公 对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.29,1:26:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是你不行啊
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.71,1:26:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那就多摸一些吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.54,1:27:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,让我更湿吧
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.49,1:27:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股的小穴完全看见了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.23,1:27:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,老公都没有看过呢
Dialogue: 0,1:27:45.43,1:27:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,多张开一些
Dialogue: 0,1:27:50.64,1:27:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,让我先看到可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.77,1:27:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,多看一些
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.71,1:27:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞的地方 多看一些
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.45,1:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.99,1:28:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,请多舔一些
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.86,1:28:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让我更湿一些
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.23,1:28:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多舔一些
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.97,1:28:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好有感觉
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.58,1:29:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,老公也这样舔吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.91,1:29:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,多舔一些
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.86,1:29:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,被老公看见很不好吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.55,1:29:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.01,1:29:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:29:43.42,1:29:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,爽的受不了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.89,1:29:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,超级爽的
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.04,1:30:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴这么湿的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.39,1:30:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,再深一些
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.26,1:30:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,吧唧吧唧的搅动起来
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.20,1:30:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.40,1:30:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别人可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.21,1:30:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,超级湿的呢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.24,1:31:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,更多...更湿一些...
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.81,1:31:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,更多...
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.17,1:32:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好淫荡啊
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.62,1:33:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,好爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.49,1:34:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.49,1:34:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,又大又肥又硬的...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.37,1:34:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,热热的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:28.23,1:34:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,插进我湿湿的小穴吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.05,1:34:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老公的
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.45,1:34:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的肉棒插我吧
Dialogue: 0,1:34:53.59,1:34:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,很爽吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:38.84,1:35:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这么想要吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:55.39,1:35:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,想要怎么样呢?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:01.93,1:36:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,大大的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.80,1:36:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,让我的小穴吞没吧
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.14,1:36:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.21,1:36:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老公的
Dialogue: 0,1:36:20.35,1:36:23.82,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公的更大的...更硬的...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:24.62,1:36:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,更长的肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.69,1:36:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,第一见的人 肉棒也可以的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.09,1:36:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不是老公的...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.83,1:36:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这个就好
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.70,1:36:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的...
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.43,1:36:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不能满足啊！
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.64,1:36:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这么想被插吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.77,1:36:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股拿出来
Dialogue: 0,1:37:03.19,1:37:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,多翘一些
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.27,1:37:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要插入了哦 看着吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.54,1:37:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.95,1:37:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,张开吧
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.76,1:37:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了 快点插我
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.63,1:37:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.83,1:37:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.58,1:37:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.78,1:38:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识的人的肉棒可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.78,1:38:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,只要大就可以了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.00,1:38:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,还没进去呢
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.33,1:38:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.47,1:38:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.74,1:38:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这个肉棒可以吧
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.50,1:38:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,想要高潮吗
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.97,1:39:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我在忍着呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.78,1:39:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,更多...更多的插我
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.45,1:39:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,插到深处
Dialogue: 0,1:39:11.98,1:39:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,让我的小穴 又湿又滑
Dialogue: 0,1:39:27.47,1:39:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.27,1:39:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.81,1:39:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,又大又硬的肉棒 很爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:39:47.35,1:39:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的不行
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.95,1:39:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不认识的人 大肉棒才最爽
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.79,1:40:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,真爽啊
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.42,1:41:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,插得好快乐
Dialogue: 0,1:42:05.49,1:42:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:07.36,1:42:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,被老公知道了怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.36,1:42:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.57,1:42:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.50,1:42:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,1:42:26.98,1:42:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,比老公的更大...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:31.38,1:42:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,更爽吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.19,1:42:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不对
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.93,1:42:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.26,1:42:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老公的肉棒
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.21,1:42:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你老公道歉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.55,1:43:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老公对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:43:05.42,1:43:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是说实话
